videos.description: Syracuse punter Sterling Hofrichter handles the high snap and simply walks out of the end zone for the safety.
videos.headline: A high snap leads to a safety on Syracuse punt

videos.description: Syracuse DE Chris Slayton leaps to knock down the backward pass and cause a fumble that his teammate Brandon Barry pounces on.
videos.headline: Slayton swats away the screen pass to force a turnover for Syracuse

videos.description: Ty Lee runs it in from 14 yards out for MTSU's first touchdown
videos.headline: Lee cuts it up the wide-open hole and strolls in for the score

videos.description: Dontae Strickland punches it in from one-yard out to give the Orange the lead.
videos.headline: Strickland powers his way in for Syracuse TD

videos.description: Sean Riley muffed the punt to give the ball right back to MTSU .
videos.headline: Syracuse muffs punt to give MTSU great field position

videos.description: Brent Stockstill finds Richie James for the tying score, after Syracuse muffed the previous punt.
videos.headline: MTSU scores with an easy strike after the turnover

videos.description: Brent Stockstill and Ty Lee hook up again for easy 48-yard score.
videos.headline: Stockstill finds Lee again for TD and MTSU lead

videos.description: QB Eric Dungey calls his own number on a 29-yard TD run to tie the game.
videos.headline: Dungey runs right up the middle to tie game

videos.description: WR Shane Tucker soars in for the Blue Raiders score to regain the lead.
videos.headline: Tucker does his best Superman impression into the end zone

videos.description: Reed Blankenship comes up with the diving interception to give ball back to MTSU.
videos.headline: Blankenship lays out for MTSU interception
